sadly there are multiple steps of data movement involved, so thats the main reason its not immediate
1. first data should get to official warframe mobile API by DE
2. then middleware parser from WFCD crew kicks in (`warframe-items` repo on github) to organize it and consolidate with some data from warframe community Wiki
3. then we get it and do small sorting to provide small efficient payload (since original source is excessively large for general use)
4. your wfinfo will get the small payload when u click refresh or restart wfinfo
